sam u ove slike i u ovu kuću.

960
01:11:46,167 --> 01:11:47,750
Posle možemo u turu... -Važi.

961
01:11:47,833 --> 01:11:50,083
Šta ćeš da piješ? -Bilo šta.

962
01:11:50,375 --> 01:11:51,375
Tekilu?

963
01:11:51,583 --> 01:11:54,458
