Dobro, hajde sad.

966
01:12:03,292 --> 01:12:06,417
Tekila za čavelu i za proslavu našeg susreta.

967
01:12:06,500 --> 01:12:07,417
Da.

968
01:12:13,917 --> 01:12:15,458
Oduševljen sam tvojom kućom.

969
01:12:16,708 --> 01:12:18,083
Gde ti živiš sad?

970
01:12:19,042 --> 01:12:20,250
U Buenos Ajresu.

971
