U Buenos Ajresu imaš strica...

972
01:12:23,625 --> 01:12:26,167
Da. Otišao sam '85-e.

973
01:12:27,208 --> 01:12:28,292
Tako rano?

974
01:12:28,833 --> 01:12:29,792
Da.

975
01:12:31,625 --> 01:12:34,583
Hoćeš sada rezime ili bolje posle?

976
01:12:37,208 --> 01:12:39,292
Živeli!

977
01:12:42,875 --> 01:12:43,958
Uf...

978
01:12:45,208 --> 01:12:46,125
Rezime.

979
01:12:46,208 --> 01:12:49,750
Nakon našeg raskida, bio sam
s roditeljima godinu dana.

980
01:12:50,500 --> 01:12:53,750
